# BOB's Super Claw — secrets box (TEMPLATE)
#
# This template is COMMITTED. It lists every key the system uses, with
# NO values. The real box lives next to it as secrets.env and is
# gitignored — it never gets committed or pushed anywhere public.
#
# Set it up once per machine:
#
#   node scripts/secrets-box.mjs init
#   # creates secrets/secrets.env + ensures it is gitignored,
#   # then edit secrets/secrets.env and paste your real keys
#
# secrets/secrets.env is the ONE local home for your API keys. Never
# paste a key anywhere else — not in code, not in a workflow file, not
# in openclaw.json (that file uses {env:VAR} placeholders on purpose).
#
# Commands (see: node scripts/secrets-box.mjs help):
#   node scripts/secrets-box.mjs init     set up the box + gitignore it
#   node scripts/secrets-box.mjs list     show which keys are set (masked)
#   node scripts/secrets-box.mjs check    verify the box is gitignored
#   node scripts/secrets-box.mjs push     push gateway keys to Fly secrets
#   eval "$(node scripts/secrets-box.mjs export)"   load keys into a shell
#
# Format: KEY=VALUE, one per line. '#' starts a comment. No quotes
# needed; the whole rest of the line is the value.

# --- Required by the gateway (push sends these to Fly app secrets) ---
# Bitdeer master API key — powers chat, embeddings and image models.
# Get one from https://www.bitdeer.ai/ai-cloud (AI Inference → API Keys).
BITDEER_API_KEY=
# Gateway auth token — authenticates API calls to the gateway itself.
OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=
# Discord bot token — reserved for future channel wiring.
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=
# Firecrawl key — web search + web fetch tools.
FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=
# Steel.dev key — hardcore browser MCP server.
STEEL_API_KEY=
# Webhook wake token — must differ from the gateway auth token.
HOOKS_TOKEN=
# Cloudflare account ID (paired with CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN).
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
# Cloudflare API token.
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
# Railway project token.
RAILWAY_TOKEN=
# Telegram bot token (plugin currently disabled; keep for re-enabling).
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=

# --- Deploy / infra (NOT pushed to the Fly app) ---------------------
# Fly.io deploy token — used by flyctl and the deploy workflow.
FLY_API_TOKEN=
# Fly app name. push/check target this app.
OPENCLAW_APP_NAME=openclawomega-ace36e

# --- Optional -------------------------------------------------------
# GitHub token — lets the event poller watch commits and CI.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
